{"tid":838196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錯把霧霾當成海市蜃樓　中國網友傻呼奇觀","createTime":"2018-09-27T02:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T07:46:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd524b3554ea82263139cdc19dfadef328c0e71","tid":838196,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"中國河南開封市上週五（21日）驚傳出現「海市蜃樓」，從目擊者拍下的影片可見，當時市區的天空大部分壟罩在灰暗中，但在陽光露出的區域，能見到一棟高樓的灰色陰影，如同「海市蜃樓」。影片曝光後，中國網友驚為奇觀，相關影片和照片在網路上受到瘋傳。不過，開封市氣象台隨後澄清，當地的「海市蜃樓」只是霧霾，大霧散去後，原本的大樓灰影，也露出全貌，證實是一棟「貨真價實」的大樓，早前只是被霧霾壟罩，才只隱約露出樓頂。<br />\n <br />\n「海市蜃樓」的說法被戳破後，中國網友紛紛表示：「河南大騙子」、「真丟臉，素質堪憂」、「你家旁邊有沒有這麼棟樓自己不知道嗎？」、「成功的拉低了中國人的智商」，也有人感嘆：「今天的霧霾又這麼嚴重」。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180926/640_a7f3c01332baf3d2411a045d27ae3852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180926%2F640_a7f3c01332baf3d2411a045d27ae3852.jpg&h=73b0212d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180926/640_d2a2e838d15a621a3125b90e97893d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180926%2F640_d2a2e838d15a621a3125b90e97893d83.jpg&h=15fc9f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180926/1436400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180926%2F1436400&d=%2FEtv7qlDusZBW5FGm0Xr6wtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=3c80a470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180926%2F1436400&h=6f828790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180926/1436400</a>"},{"pid":"8b44765047ddfd04b4a681f6a4c98407fec1320d","tid":838196,"uid":18167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"相關新聞:<br />\n<br />\n中國空污太嚴重... 研究：恐損害人體智力！<br />